Reasoning: 
- cs.SD (Sound): The paper focuses on keyword spotting in audio signals, which falls under the domain of sound processing. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper proposes a neural approach for keyword spotting, which involves natural language processing techniques. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper aims to simplify the pipeline of building a production-quality KWS system, which involves system design and control. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes an end-to-end neural approach for KWS, which involves machine learning techniques. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a novel approach for KWS using attention-based end-to-end models, which falls under the domain of artificial intelligence.
